{Speech 2}{}{Hello there.}
{Speech 2 Answer 24}{}{It seems to me that yours croupier and guards are very suspicious to everybody. Has something happened?}
{Speech 2 Answer 25}{}{The thief is found. He had 500 coins in his pockets. What should I do?}
{Speech 2 Answer 23}{}{I've succeded in finding out the secret ingredient of Bob's booze,}
{Speech 2 Answer 8}{}{I've come to take Jame's payment. He said 400 coins.}
{Speech 2 Answer 7}{}{Do you know anything about the ghost in the deserted house?}
