{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Hello. Got a job for me?}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{Do you want me to deliver "something"?}
{Speech 2 Answer 26}{}{Не надо ли опять доставить "кое-что"?}
{Speech 2 Answer 6}{}{Here's what you've asked to bring.}
{Speech 2 Answer 20}{}{Here's Bob's booze.}
{Speech 2 Answer 10}{}{Got anything to drink?}
{Speech 2 Answer 11}{}{Got anything to drink?}
