{Speech 2 Answer 200}{}{Слушай, Леанна, я хотел@sex@||а| спросить, ты не видела одного человека?@@Слушай, Леанна, я хотел@sex@||а| спросиить, ты ничего не слышала об одном человеке?@@Я ищу одного человека, ничего не слышала о нем, Леанна?}
{Speech 3}{}{Could you do some business for me?}
{Speech 3 Answer 4}{}{Of course.}
{Speech 3 Answer 15}{}{Another time.}
{Speech 4}{}{Go to New Reno and take something from Kitty, If you do this I give you 500 coins.}
{Speech 4 Answer 5}{}{What exactly?}
{Speech 4 Answer 15}{}{No, I'm busy,}
{Speech 5}{}{She knows. Just tell her "I need something for somebody," and she will understand you're the right guy.}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{Ok, no problem.}
{Speech 6}{}{Oh, great! Take your 500 coins,}
{Speech 7}{}{Ghost? Let me think... Ask Mom. She knows more about ghosts.}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{Ok, I'll ask her.}
{Speech 8}{}{Yeah, of course. Here's the money.}
{Speech 9}{}{It seems I'm a bit short of funds. But you can come later.}
{Speech 10}{}{Certainly, only 5 coins.}
{Speech 10 Answer 14}{}{Great, one portion for me.}
{Speech 10 Answer 13}{}{Great, one portion for me.}
{Speech 10 Answer 15}{}{I don't have enough money.}
{Speech 10 Answer 16}{}{Don't you think that your alcohol is overpriced a bit?}
{Speech 10 Answer 15*}{}{I'd better come next time.}
{Speech 11}{}{Sorry, we ran out of alcohol.}
{Speech 13}{}{Sorry, we don't serve for free.@@You'd better try another time.}
{Speech 14}{}{One portion of superb beer!@@Your beer, be healthy!}
{Speech 15}{}{You are welcome at any time.@@Come again.}
{Speech 16}{}{Well that isn't exatly...  Ok it is so. I can't do anything. If I reduce my prices, they would be equal to the cost price.}
{Speech 16 Answer 17}{}{That's a pity.}
{Speech 17}{}{We don't know each other well, but I can offer you one easy job.}
{Speech 17 Answer 18}{}{So, what's this?}
{Speech 18}{}{Go to Klamath and find Wiskey Bob. He has his own alcohol fabric. Buy several bottles of his booze and bring them to me. I want to check, maybe he dilutes his booze with water...}
{Speech 18 Answer Exit}{}{Alright.}
{Speech 18 Answer Exit*}{}{I don't want to do it.}
{Speech 18 Answer Exit**}{}{Lets discuss this another time.}
{Speech 19}{}{Get out, dumbass!}
