{Speech 23}{}{Salt? [Leanna seems to be confused] Well, it's good news. Take 300 coins for your efforts.}
{Speech 24}{}{You're very attentive. Maybe you can help us. Money began to disappear from our clients' pockets. It seems that a pickpocketer works in our bar, but we can't find him. Will you help find him?}
